ssure, or are taking any prescription meds.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="97d76fec-a64a-46ce-b9bd-6d24e9712581" class="r-x83jki"></div><div data-rid="301f20f9-5801-4074-a2bb-ca687f3ab890" class="r-1fup5y0" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="4a077f3c-11b9-4cc5-b82b-0826cb9eb28a" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R7cj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1o1bawc"><div data-rid="b0aaa70b-9eeb-48b2-a5ed-a6bd18767bb6" class="r-1wmv7ez alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What scientific research is the formulation based on?</p></span></div><div data-rid="8a7ce370-667b-4a28-8374-396a24a1f337" class="r-13vj0ml" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1cgjf5v" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R7cj2:"><div data-rid="ff690a00-01eb-4dc1-b9ff-bd32f2552ec4" class="r-1rn8k6v"><div data-rid="edd46bf3-8652-4f6a-b113-f8855de6f95b" class="r-1a13oi alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>See the many articles we've written on Methylene Blue&nbsp;<a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://troscriptions.com/search?type=product,page,article&q=methylene%20blue*"><u>here</u></a>!</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="575189c8-4569-4f0c-9c01-bb5d941a55df" class="r-1ctpep3"></div><div data-rid="dd2848a6-a70b-4d4b-a23b-b5c8e66ad1b1" class="r-y4hi5f" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="377218d1-3274-4b16-ad52-4fe46db05ebe" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rbcj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-nnir9i"><div data-rid="7088167f-2f4f-47cc-8c91-4177f1ae5e5b" class="r-6d8elr alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Will it turn my mouth blue?</p></span></div><div data-rid="cae9ab21-966e-46b5-87ee-5847adc854ac" class="r-1raz3e7" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-b1b5sw" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rbcj2:"><div data-rid="d3f16b10-bee1-4da8-b0a2-95ce6e6311d7" class="r-1j3kg15"><div data-rid="a2e3a60e-f341-4dfb-8a78-0767c159533d" class="r-1m5nd5c alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>If used as a buccal troche, discoloration can vary between 2–24 hours. To reduce it, rinse first with a 1:1 vinegar and water solution, then with ¼ tsp baking soda in 4 fl oz water for a few minutes. Vitamin C and hot liquids can also help — or simply swallow the troche to avoid discoloration altogether.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="97c2039f-e8e1-41ab-a4fb-d20927e15f19" class="r-1am9enb"></div><div data-rid="eb5c2a41-15bd-44b9-b75d-7f2064ea862f" class="r-mxgowg" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="dc3ad5d8-3a01-4bbd-97fc-862b76beab97" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rfcj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-oawon3"><div data-rid="2e14c327-4532-49bd-b8fc-39128c829add" class="r-g9z8qq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Can I see the 3rd party testing?</p></span></div><div data-rid="36e72f22-56fd-4664-b3e2-4f5c126583b1" class="r-1to4p3" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-igxg9p" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rfcj2:"><div data-rid="6392410e-a572-4eac-ac5d-6c83639e5063" class="r-a3l0sb"><div data-rid="6fd31de6-5448-4929-8836-d1afcdf07a2f" class="r-1x41biy alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Email <a href="mailto:buccalup@troscriptions.com">buccalup@troscriptions.com</a> and we'll be happy to share this with you!</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="079eea9e-f119-4a98-975f-46d30eb25dde" class="r-pgp91k"></div><div data-rid="6f8d261e-b978-42ad-8e0c-75bb3a479647" class="r-1x4dl14" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="f5de27a8-202e-497e-9dd1-57e9c6976fc0" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rjcj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1xz62my"><div data-rid="5991a3d3-b940-4a20-b212-e70288ed01b1" class="r-1en0dfn alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Why does it contain Polyethylene Glycol (PEG)?</p></span></div><div data-rid="65d7dd48-99c9-43c6-927b-2572e07ae237" class="r-10c0ah0" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-pyvqni" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rjcj2:"><div data-rid="d8f4f73e-e48c-43c9-87c1-24fd0d338d71" class="r-1s7b4py"><div data-rid="0db948ee-db3f-43ea-936d-dfe84a889277" class="r-fxyg0q alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Polyethylene Glycol is a long-established FDA-approved drug delivery method used around the world, especially by compounding pharmacists. Do not confuse polyethylene glycol with propylene glycol. The latter is antifreeze and will kill you if you drink it…so please don’t do that! </p><br><p>Our formulations use polyethylene glycol that is both non-absorbable and very low dose, meaning that it does not get absorbed into your body and it will not cause GI distress or any of those other symptoms/issues that you may have heard about.<br>For more information, please see <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://troscriptions.com/blogs/main/polyethylene-glycol-peg"><u>this article</u></a> for an in-depth explanation.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="907e235d-beef-467e-bde5-742e0e4ba349" class="r-5sxo7j"></div><div data-rid="346a6a82-a478-466b-aa9a-39606112d8ff" class="r-ruf1z2" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="3771ddc4-3d27-44cd-95ca-426759c43b3f" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rncj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-eq9ge8"><div data-rid="66b2a46f-52ab-4ae1-a34d-60ec0e4faef5" class="r-6tt4sj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How many troches am I getting?</p></span></div><div data-rid="a67de9f9-f7b8-416d-a57d-4d6f7ca561e1" class="r-1fikv4p" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-soiyss" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rncj2:"><div data-rid="84b6804a-0887-4e92-a406-a7419286b914" class="r-1s95r"><div data-rid="39e3066a-826a-4f22-a3c2-1a4a85e00782" class="r-1a2ap9z alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>There are 4 whole troches in each package and each troche can be cut into four quarters. Therefore, one pack can yield up to 16 doses, depending on your personalized needs. The troches are scored for easy titration.</p><p> </p><p>Start with 1/4 troche to 1/2 troche and increase the dosage until you reach your optimal dose.</p><p>DO NOT exceed more than 4 whole troches in a 24-hour period. </p><br><p>For Tro+ Blue, the above instructions may not apply. Please follow the directions from your healthcare provider.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="069bf0a5-6d60-4157-a501-0228784f6bc9" class="r-107b4kx"></div><div data-rid="b2d24d9c-622f-47e8-8d32-ec548687cd71" class="r-1xs45vq" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="21b0ed99-283d-4e47-bf2a-f147d0897a5f" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rrcj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1j5er29"><div data-rid="eebef745-5a77-4042-8546-318db185de9e" class="r-bdfj7k alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What is the difference between Blue Cannatine™ & Just Blue™?</p></span></div><div data-rid="2622dd16-f959-4c84-95d3-2b063b453953" class="r-1f46cnd" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-y1okbu" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rrcj2:"><div data-rid="31afc31a-116e-4edb-bdb7-162bcab70245" class="r-1cpmta2"><div data-rid="89f53828-71d5-44b4-99cb-a494c751a8cc" class="r-1x7lriv alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Blue Cannatine™ contains methylene blue (5 mg per troche), caffeine, nicotine and hemp crystals. </p><br><p>Just Blue™ contains methylene blue (16 mg per troche). </p><br><p>We created Just Blue™ based on customer requests for a nootropic that optimizes and enhances mitochondrial function without nicotine or caffeine. Blue Cannatine™ gives you more of a "kick" or "launch" in energy and focus. With Just Blue™, it is more subtle and sustained energy, focus, and endurance. </p><br><p>Check out our reviews to see our customers' experiences with both products.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="c0a2e7d8-cbab-4387-a2ce-0dc87f9da0cc" class="r-wlvoyf"></div><div data-rid="32377289-b226-4816-a090-a9942830d958" class="r-tkqpp3" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="85b41b56-5684-42d6-9f6a-0a39282d5787" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rvcj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1pyh1l9"><div data-rid="8dacc01e-4b88-423c-a5aa-12785071900e" class="r-lelema alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What does it taste like?</p></span></div><div data-rid="a98ca008-0f22-426c-9a62-0528535e557b" class="r-ieunib" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-px1oe4" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rvcj2:"><div data-rid="16bfac8b-dfe7-4c3a-bbf9-110db2636a09" class="r-i2gzwt"><div data-rid="af14a803-671f-421c-b0de-7f1ba75fcf08" class="r-vdcp6 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Our proprietary Bitter-Bloc™ formula eliminates the bitter Methylene Blue taste often found in liquid droppers — plus, we’ve added a hint of mint for freshness.</p><br><p>Methylene Blue naturally has a bitter flavor, so if you prefer to avoid it, you can simply swallow it since it’s 100% bioavailable!</p></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><style>@import url(https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600;700;800;900;950&family=Inter:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600;700;800;900;950)</style></div>
